entry.title: Ljubljana (Wikivoyage recommendations)
entry.content:
Ljubljana

Destination of the month

It's a pleasure to just stroll around in Slovenia's little capital with a lot of greenery and smaller attractions.

entry.title: Diablo Range (Wikivoyage recommendations)
entry.content:
Diablo Range

Destination of the month

California's Diablo Range, with Mount Diablo, reservoirs, and rugged terrain, but also oak trees on rolling hills, is an enjoyable destination for both serious hikers and casual tourists.

entry.title: Functionalist architecture in Finland (Wikivoyage recommendations)
entry.content:
Functionalist architecture in Finland

Featured Travel Topic

Functionalism became a popular style among Finnish architects a century ago and the country is one of the best destinations to admire these simple, streamlined and often white buildings.
